{"word":"Parents","slug":"parents","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Parents</b> Covenant benefits of, entailed on children<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=6&verse=18'>Gen 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=6'>Exo 20:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=103&verse=17'>Psa 103:17</a><br/> Curses entailed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=5'>Exo 20:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=5'>Lev 20:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=14&verse=20'>Isa 14:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=9&verse=14'>Jer 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=5&verse=7'>Lam 5:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=45'>Eze 16:45</a><br/> Involved in children's wickedness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=36'>1Sa 2:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=4&verse=22'>1Sa 4:22</a><br/> Partiality of:<br/> - Isaac for Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=28'>Gen 25:28</a> <br/> - Rebekah for Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=28'>Gen 25:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=17'>Gen 27:17</a> <br/> - Jacob for Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=33&verse=2'>Gen 33:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=3'>Gen 37:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=48&verse=22'>Gen 48:22</a> <br/> - Jacob for Benjamin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=4'>Gen 42:4</a><br/><a href='S:Partiality'>Partiality</a> <br/> Parental affection exemplified:<br/> - By Hagar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=16'>Gen 21:16</a> <br/> - By Rebekah's mother<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=55'>Gen 24:55</a> <br/> - By Isaac and Rebekah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=28'>Gen 25:28</a> <br/> - By Isaac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=27'>Gen 27:27</a> <br/> - By Laban<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=28'>Gen 31:28</a> <br/> - By Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=4'>Gen 37:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=4'>Gen 42:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=38'>Gen 42:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=14'>Gen 43:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=45&verse=28'>Gen 45:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=48&verse=11'>Gen 48:11</a> <br/> - By Moses' mother<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2'>Exo 2</a> <br/> - By Naomi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=9'>Rth 1:9</a> <br/> - By Hannah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=19'>1Sa 2:19</a> <br/> - By David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=23'>2Sa 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=39'>2Sa 13:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=1'>2Sa 14:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=33'>2Sa 14:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=5'>2Sa 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=13'>2Sa 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=33'>2Sa 18:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles